eshmun.modelchecker

Class KripkeModelChecker

  • java.lang.Object
    • eshmun.modelchecker.AbstractModelChecker
      • eshmun.modelchecker.KripkeModelChecker

  • public class KripkeModelChecker
extends AbstractModelChecker
    The class represents a Model Checker, it uses the visitor pattern.

    1.0
    Author:
    Ali Cherri, Kinan Dak Al Bab

    • Method Detail

      • run

        public boolean run(AbstractExpression specifications)
        Model checks against the given specifications, the structure to be model checked is provided in the constructor and it must be a KripkeStructure.

        This method should be overridden in the concrete model checker.

        Specified by:
        run in class AbstractModelChecker
        Parameters:
        specifications - CTL specifications to model-check against, in simplified version.
        Returns:
        true if the structure satisfies the specifications, false otherwise.
